70
00:06:47,620 --> 00:06:49,370
No quiero desperdiciarlo así.

71
00:06:56,830 --> 00:06:58,500
¡Sin futuro!

72
00:07:02,870 --> 00:07:04,410
Me disculpa.

73
00:07:08,950 --> 00:07:10,910
