254
00:26:29,950 --> 00:26:30,870
Toey.

255
00:26:32,870 --> 00:26:33,580
¡Demasiado!

256
00:26:35,330 --> 00:26:36,330
¿Sí?  Ah gracias.

257
00:26:40,660 --> 00:26:41,870
¿Sigues cansado?

258
00:26:53,620 --> 00:26:55,160
